snippet.title: Beavis And Butt Head In Quest To Score // SAGE 2024 Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/beavis-and-butt-head-in-quest-to-score.2129/

Beavis and Butt-head can't afford tickets to a concert that they want to go to as the tickets are 20bucks and unfortunately they only had 20 cents. With a goal in mind to score and to do things that don't suck Beavis and Butt-Head set off to get $20 to pay for the tickets and to acquire the delicacy known as Nachos as the venue didn't sell it.

Developed by Beavis1993
